{"tid":867760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【10月18日】第4次川中島之戰","createTime":"2018-10-19T02:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T05:57:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be5b889b174b966aa81e08a772b92d4ddb73d36b","tid":867760,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/ArticleFile/20181018/2018101722505713925.jpg?id=309363&amp;m=v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FArticleFile%2F20181018%2F2018101722505713925.jpg%3Fid%3D309363%26m%3Dv&h=d0f6d860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1561年10月18日（永祿4年9月10日），「甲斐之虎」武田信玄與「越後之龍」上杉謙信在川中島地區交戰，雙方死傷逾7000人，為日本戰國史上最著名、傷亡率最高的會戰之一。<br />\n<br />\n武田家與上杉家為爭奪區域霸權，先後曾在川中島進行過5次會戰，最著名的是這場又名「八幡原之戰」的第4次川中島之戰。是役兵力占優勢的武田軍兵分兩路，希望夾擊上杉軍，結果上杉謙信率全軍直接奔襲武田信玄本營，殺死多名武田軍重要將領，最後在武田援軍趕到後撤退。雖然武田軍傷亡較重，不過上杉軍未能達成其戰略目標，雙方皆稱己方獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n由於力量勢均力敵，戰事傷亡又過於慘重，武田與上杉在此戰後避免直接衝突，包括第5次川中島之戰在內皆未發生交戰。在主將知名度、軍隊規模與慘烈戰況影響之下，第4次川中島之戰成為日本戰國時代最著名的會戰之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/309363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FNews%2F309363&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1942e97c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/309363</a>"},{"pid":"aae86270522caf71433ae3b77949a616d7b6e30c","tid":867760,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:37:26.000Z","msg":"溫馨提示：過程詳細只有《甲陽軍鑑》寫<br />\n實際戰果靠信玄、謙信既書信及後續發展推測"},{"pid":"df23aeefbe24e24b0cf5fd6160954afaaf608426","tid":867760,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"先得嗰7000人已經係傷亡率最高<br />\n難怪有人話日本戰國既所謂打仗只係兩條村械鬥"},{"pid":"b211740c1e85f27103d4d7bb089f1d2791e824a1","tid":867760,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df23aeefbe24e24b0cf5fd6160954afaaf608426","tid":867760,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"先得嗰7000人已經係傷亡率最高<br />\n難怪有人話日本戰國既所謂打仗只係兩條村械鬥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"村長打鬥論被人駁左好耐喇中"},{"pid":"22313bacb4b1e46e687b5c28c304f3a949d98ae9","tid":867760,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df23aeefbe24e24b0cf5fd6160954afaaf608426","tid":867760,"uid":66260,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"先得嗰7000人已經係傷亡率最高<br />\n難怪有人話日本戰國既所謂打仗只係兩條村械鬥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"同大陸比較咩"},{"pid":"5226b6a640fed7c13af38bceca3f0bd4f294875f","tid":867760,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"萬曆朝鮮之役<br />\n<br />\n兵力<br />\n<br />\n大明：約75,000人<br />\n朝鮮：190,000人<br />\n（包含民兵）\t<br />\n日本：約141,500人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷亡與損失<br />\n<br />\n大明：約3萬人<br />\n朝鮮：約12萬人<br />\n日本：超過17萬人<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮平民約100萬人死亡"},{"pid":"82a2222c2b8da26cd0e2a5c85417e47458e5bcfd","tid":867760,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5226b6a640fed7c13af38bceca3f0bd4f294875f","tid":867760,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"萬曆朝鮮之役<br />\n<br />\n兵力<br />\n<br />\n大明：約75,000人<br />\n朝鮮：190,000人<br />\n（包含民兵）\t<br />\n日本：約141,500人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傷亡與損失<br />\n<br />\n大明：約3萬人<br />\n朝鮮：約12萬人<br />\n日本：超過17萬人<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮平民約100萬人死亡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:02:45.000Z","msg":"14萬兵力死17萬人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245641e2a1d2358f6a53f4f4ba984dba87dc8488","tid":867760,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82a2222c2b8da26cd0e2a5c85417e47458e5bcfd","tid":867760,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5226b6a640fed7c13af38bceca3f0bd4f294875f","tid":867760,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:58:4